      "title": "Add rate limiting to public API endpoints",
      "description": "Implement per-user and per-IP rate limiting on all public API routes to prevent abuse. Use Redis sliding window algorithm.\n\nLimits:\n- Authenticated users: 1000 req/min\n- Unauthenticated: 60 req/min",
